snippet.textDisplay: The risk of anything related to vitamin d doses above 4000IU is ONLY present if you're NOT taking k2 vitamin. In other words: if you take between 4,000 to 10,000IU and also take vitamin K2 (200mg) the risk is virtually non existent.
